| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2360 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1cb88601-a5f0-5d14-8991-bbe07a5a1353"
